settings.title: KH Glow Laser Facial
settings.description: A non-invasive, restorative treatment using a laser, designed to treat fine lines and wrinkles, tighten pores and diffuse redness, all while improving the skin's texture and tone. Areas of the face, neck and body can be treated with no downtime. We recommend this treatment to clients seeking vibrant and healthy looking skin before a big event.

settings.title: KH Trilogy Laser Facial
settings.description: A carefully curated triple-tier approach to skin rejuvenation. Our laser technician begins with a round of IPL, followed by a round of Glow, and concludes the Trilogy with a secondary IPL pass. The Glow portion gently heats the dermis to improve skin texture and encourages new collagen production while the IPL portion improves the superficial appearance of the skin by addressing pigmentation, redness, brown spots and other signs of aging with minimal discomfort. These treatments when used in sync with one another maximize the efficiency of the treatment to produce optimal results in just one session.

settings.description_left: This laser treatment works by creating millions of microscopic treatment zones in the skin, replacing damaged skin with healthy, younger looking tissue. The Clear + Brilliant is a non-surgical and non-invasive fractional skin resurfacing service that targets the natural results of aging by promoting improved tone and texture. This maintenance treatment boasts radiant results with minimal downtime causing a youthful glow, smooth surface and a reduction in the appearance of pores. Clear + Brilliant is safe for all ages and lifestyles.
